title: Jens Johansson Discography
description:
These albums are almost nowhere to be found, I even cant order those to my country! I will still try to get the CD versions and listen it on my NAD rather than on crappy iPod.

Here is the list of albums, Jens solo and with his brother Andreas:



1991 - Fjaderlosa Tvafotingar(ep)(128kbps)
1994 - The Johansson Brothers
1995 - Ten Seasons(192kbps)
1996 - Sonic Winter
1997 - Heavy Machinery
1998 - Fission(reissue 2008)
1999 - The Last Viking
